    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>3rd-level Way of the Ascendant Dragon feature</i></p><p>You can channel draconic power to magnify your presence and imbue your unarmed strikes with the essence of a dragon's breath. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Draconic Presence\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Draconic Presence.</span> If you fail a Charisma (&amp;Reference[skill=Intimidation]) or Charisma (&amp;Reference[skill=Persuasion]) check, you can use your reaction to reroll the check, as you tap into the mighty presence of dragons. Once this feature turns a failure into a success, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Draconic Strike\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Draconic Strike.</span> When you damage a target with an unarmed strike, you can change the damage type to acid, cold, fire, lightning, or poison.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Tongue of Dragons\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Tongue of Dragons.</span> You learn to speak, read, and write @language[Draconic] or one other language of your choice.</p></li></ul></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
